"""
Algo Strategy: FSM-Based Value-Balanced NIFTY CE-PE Trading

Finite State Machine States:
  INIT → BALANCED → ROLL_LOSER → MONITOR → EXIT

Strategy:
1. Enter ATM NIFTY CE and PE positions
2. Monitor Total Trade Value (LTP × Qty) for each leg
3. If imbalance > 30% & diff > 1500: ROLL LOSING LEG (Close Loser, Sell Further OTM Strike)
4. Use Rolling to maintain constant lot size while reducing exposure
5. MONITOR state allows one-time reversal rebalance (if needed) or manual intervention
6. EXIT on persistent imbalance or risk breach

Features: DRY_RUN mode, guardrails, state persistence, detailed logging.
"""

